| 1ooooooooooooooooooo      : |USB2
|  Wi  Pi Model 5B  V1.0  fan +====
|  Fi     +---+      +---+       |
|         |RAM|      |RP1|    +====
||p       +---+      +---+    |USB3
||c      -------              +====
||i        SoC      |c|c J14     |
